  "content": "Prerequisites: Base attack bonus +4, Blind-Fight, Wisdom 19.\nBenefit: Using senses such as acute hearing and sensitivity to vibrations, you detect the location of opponents who are no more than 5 feet away from you. Invisibility and darkness are irrelevant, though it you discern incorporeal beings.",
